videos.description: Luka Garza gets the ball at the top beyond the NBA 3-point line and pulls up to sink a 3-pointer and extend Iowa's lead to 21-9 over Western Illinois.
videos.headline: Garza drains NBA 3

videos.description: Luka Garza's father happily voices his approval from the stands as Garza catches a difficult pass through defenders and flexes after he finishes the fast-break bucket.
